resources.string:
"UniMMR=AdjustedEquity /Maintenance Margin. UniMMR is the ratio we use to control the position’s risk.

Normal: uniMMR > 2, trade normally;

Low Risk: 1.5 < uniMMR <= 2, trade normally, but need to pay attention to potential liquidation;

Medium Risk: 1.2 < uniMMR <= 1.5, trade normally, but need to add more funds to avoid liquidation;

High Risk: 1.1 < uniMMR <= 1.2, trade restricted, unable to trade, withdraw and can only place reduce_only trade;

Liquidated: 1 < uniMMR <= 1.05%, liquidation is triggered.

Bankrupted: uniMMR <= 1, bankrupted."

"UniMMR=Adjusted Equity /Maintenance Margin.
Your Adjusted Equity (USD) = %1$s
Your Maintenance Margin (USD) = %2$s

UniMMR is the ratio we use to control the position's risk.

Normal: uniMMR > 2, trade normally;

Low Risk: 1.5 < uniMMR <= 2, trade normally, but need to pay attention to potential liquidation;

Medium Risk: 1.2 < uniMMR <= 1.5, trade normally, but need to add more funds to avoid liquidation;

High Risk: 1.1 < uniMMR <= 1.2, trade restricted, unable to trade, withdraw and can only place reduce_only trade;

Liquidated: 1 < uniMMR <= 1.05, liquidation is triggered.

Bankrupted: uniMMR <= 1, bankrupted."
